attributes.long-description:
2020 : The world’s economic and civil order is shaken by an unprecedented energy crisis re-igniting the arms race between the United States of America, Russia and Europe. Pick your side!

- Easy to pick up with 3 tutorial levels.
- Battle in Paris, London, etc... across 100 missions.
- Design multiplayer missions and maps.
- Upgrade your units and build a powerful army.
